text: Kalipatnam is a village in West godavari district of the Indian state Andhra Pradesh.Mandal wise list of villages in west godavari http://vlist.in/district/546.html. Lankalakoderu railway Station, Narasapur railway Station are the nearest railway stations. ==Geography== Kalipatnam is located at coordinates of . == Demographics == Census of India, Kalipatnam had a population of 11839. The total population constitute, 5832 males and 6007 females with a sex ratio of 1030 females per 1000 males. 1183 children are in the age group of 0–6 years, with sex ratio of 975. The average literacy rate stands at 68.00%. ==References== Category:Villages in West Godavari district
